      <title>泽连斯基助手希望下次乌克兰峰会将有助于结束战争</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/zelenskiy-s-aide-hopes-next-ukraine-summit-will-help-end-fighting</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰总统泽连斯基的幕僚长表示，乌克兰希望今年晚些时候举行的第二次领导人峰会为结束战争铺平道路。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/zelenskiy-s-aide-hopes-next-ukraine-summit-will-help-end-fighting</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 16:31:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>M23 叛军称他们准备尊重刚果停火协议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/m23-rebels-say-they-are-ready-to-respect-congo-cease-fire</link>
      <description><![CDATA[M23 叛军表示，他们不受本周卢旺达与刚果民主共和国签署的停火协议的约束，但他们愿意尊重该协议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/m23-rebels-say-they-are-ready-to-respect-congo-cease-fire</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 16:00:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>俄罗斯释放美国记者，与克里姆林宫特工进行大规模交换</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/russia-releases-us-reporter-in-major-swap-for-kremlin-agents</link>
      <description><![CDATA[俄罗斯释放了《华尔街日报》记者埃文·格什科维奇，并监禁了克里姆林宫的批评者，这是俄罗斯与西方几十年来最大规模的囚犯交换，以换取总统弗拉基米尔·普京寻找的一名重要刺客。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/russia-releases-us-reporter-in-major-swap-for-kremlin-agents</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 15:39:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>斯塔默警告社交媒体公司注意其在英国暴力事件中扮演的角色</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/starmer-warns-social-media-firms-about-role-in-uk-violence</link>
      <description><![CDATA[本周，英国极右翼示威者在全英国引发暴力骚乱，似乎是由网上的错误信息引发的。基尔·斯塔默 (Keir Starmer) 警告社交媒体公司，犯罪就发生在“你们的场所”内。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/starmer-warns-social-media-firms-about-role-in-uk-violence</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 15:37:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>卡马拉·哈里斯的受欢迎程度和降息暗示正在损害“特朗普交易”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/harris-powell-double-act-leads-to-unwinding-of-trump-trades</link>
      <description><![CDATA[卡马拉·哈里斯在美国大选民意调查中的人气飙升，以及美联储即将开始降息的可能性飙升，对所谓的特朗普交易造成了双重打击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/harris-powell-double-act-leads-to-unwinding-of-trump-trades</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 15:12:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马杜罗承诺尊重巴西对阿根廷大使馆的控制</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/milei-thanks-brazil-for-stepping-in-amid-venezuela-embassy-spat</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据一位知情的巴西官员透露，委内瑞拉向巴西承诺，将尊重阿根廷驻加拉加斯大使馆的完整性，包括在外交使团内避难的六名尼古拉斯·马杜罗政府反对者。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/milei-thanks-brazil-for-stepping-in-amid-venezuela-embassy-spat</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 01 Aug 2024 13:52:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哈里斯的移民计划过于雄心勃勃，引发特朗普的攻击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-01/how-kamala-harris-immigration-failures-set-up-attacks-by-trump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[卡玛拉·哈里斯为解决移民根本原因所做的努力现在已成为她竞选总统过程中最大的负担之一。]]></description>
